At least one man died outside OR Tambo International airport drop area on Monday. The incident which looked like a hijacking , It is alleged that a VW Golf 7 without registration stopped at the arrivals and departure s terminal on Jones Street. &nbsp;It is reported that an unconfirmed number of men stepped out and opened fire. An eyewitness said Like you see in the movies the black vehicle, before it stopped, three of the doors were open and people jumped out and started shooting. When I went past there, there was a body lying on the road. It looked like it had been shot to pieces. &nbsp;